{"tid":657060,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人都會同我一樣？","createTime":"2018-05-07T18:56:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-08T11:50:31.000Z","uid":38469,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9fb87fd752dc0c8bb0d387df6c6a6d795becd09b","tid":657060,"uid":38469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T18:56:20.000Z","msg":"聽某一首歌嘅時候就會諗翻人生某一個階段，然後就會好懷緬嗰個階段<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n聽&lsquo;&lsquo;不知不覺已大個&rsquo;&rsquo;就諗翻起中學畢業嗰振；聽&lsquo;&lsquo;煩擾中起舞&rsquo;&rsquo;就諗翻起啱啱升上HD嗰振：聽&lsquo;&lsquo;Lifehouse&rsquo;&rsquo;啲歌就諗翻起同啲frd周圍去玩嘅時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"898e5907f62fa1c8b97704ffb35aced53a519e90","tid":657060,"uid":38469,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T18:57:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/025648_e19b4872c8586b0d0773d6941242a3fb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F08%2F025648_e19b4872c8586b0d0773d6941242a3fb.png&h=e7a78945&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依加聽緊呢首就係之前同ex分手日日瞓唔着聽嘅一首<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf0d9cfe1da35249603dcae32e8ce66f56dc7b1","tid":657060,"uid":29719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T19:28:45.000Z","msg":"會<br />\n例如某首歌係夏天聽嘅時候有好深刻回憶 <br />\n之後就會覺得個首歌只係適合係夏天聽"},{"pid":"e1cd6cdfcc1932035dd18d1555bb5240ce7128c1","tid":657060,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T19:36:30.000Z","msg":"會 因為果段時間就係係咁聽果首歌"},{"pid":"d306496ae46b0d269a5adcfeae125e6f3da44ccc","tid":657060,"uid":38469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adf0d9cfe1da35249603dcae32e8ce66f56dc7b1","tid":657060,"uid":29719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T19:28:45.000Z","msg":"會<br />\n例如某首歌係夏天聽嘅時候有好深刻回憶 <br />\n之後就會覺得個首歌只係適合係夏天聽"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-